    <item>
      <title>投资者等待利率线索，新兴市场小幅走低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/emerging-markets-edge-lower-with-investors-poised-for-rate-clues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于大宗商品价格暴跌，且交易员关注一系列经济数据，这些数据将为美联储的降息路径提供更多线索，新兴市场资产连续第二天下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/emerging-markets-edge-lower-with-investors-poised-for-rate-clues</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 09:30:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>希腊银行在升级后股价上涨，大幅削减 AT1 成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/greek-bank-slashes-at1-cost-as-it-rides-post-upgrade-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家希腊银行大幅削减了资本成本，凸显了在信用评级升级和人们对最具风险的银行债务的广泛需求下该国资产的上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/greek-bank-slashes-at1-cost-as-it-rides-post-upgrade-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 09:11:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
